-- Syrian Forces Kill 15 Prisoners at Aleppo Central: Al Arabiya
-- B y   Z a i d   S a b a h
-- 2012-07-24T02:42:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-24/syrian-forces-kill-15-prisoners-at-aleppo-central-al-arabiya.html
Syrian government forces killed 15
prisoners and injured 45 during a riot at Aleppo Central Prison
last night,  Al Arabiya  television reported, citing Abu Abdullah
al-Halabi, an activist from Aleppo. The prison has more than
8,000 inmates, he said, according to Al Arabiya.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zaid Sabah Abd Alhamid in Washington at 
 zalhamid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
